@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rdlrpl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.76)) * (0.64 + (v0 + 0.21 / v1 + 0.60)))
    tmp = 0.56
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.61) - v1))
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.45 * tmp + 0.14) * v2) * wp.exp(0.87))
    v0 = 0.32
    v1 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin((v2 * wp.abs(tmp + 0.13)))
    v1 = (v2 / v1)
    data[tid] = v0
